divs: Sighting DetailsFor the last 20 minutes we have been seeing moving stars and flashing white light seen all over the sky. It is almost continuous. Every few seconds. A bright white shooting star as well. Multiple small airplanes flying fairly high. These planes are going E to W. Every 3 mins. or so. The flashing light doesn't appear to be lightening as it is very clear out tonight. About as clear as it ever gets. Seeing some chemtrails now though. The high planes I think. Problem with our magnetic field, maybe? So much activity in the sky all happening at once. Thank you.
